### SPI Apple Developer account

SPI already has a developer account for use by associated projects to
publish on the various Apple App Stores. At the moment the small
yearly cost (~US$100) is allocated to the 0.ad associated project as
they are the only user, but additional projects could be changed pro-rata.

### Additional Domain registrar

Stephen Frost says this has been more-or-less handled and the project in question will just be using Gandi.

Célestin Matte is working with them to get that all set up and going,
so I don't think we have any action to take on that.

## Any other business

